title: Prop-001 - What %, if any, of Magicat royalties should buyback boo?
body:
This proposal is for our upcoming Magicat NFT series to have royalties on paintswap.finance and artion.io to be set at 5% with the possibility of some amount being used to buyback BOO automatically on every sale and distributed to xBOO.

What should the percent breakdown be of the 5% royalty? Basically, what percent should go to developers and what percent to xBOO?

Keep in mind you can make multiple choices for this vote as it is ranked choice voting! This means you can set priorities for your vote, basically 1st choice, 2nd choice etc

Read more about our upcoming generative NFT series Magicats here: https://spookyswap.medium.com/spookyswap-generative-nft-development-update-5e8883c7ec86

Contract for royalties here:
https://github.com/SpookySwap/spooky-nft-contracts/blob/master/contracts/MagicatRoyalties.sol
